---
title: Lemongrass Pork Burgers with Carrot Fries and Sriracha Mayo
description: We love how Thai cuisine embraces some seriously fun and funky flavors, like fragrant fresh herbs, citrusy lemongrass, and fiery chiles. So when we were looking to create a burger that goes beyond the ordinary, those unique ingredients proved to be just the inspiration we needed. They’re woven throughout the pork patties, giving them an intensely aromatic profile that pairs well with the sweet and tender carrot fries on the side.
